ever serves HTML.\n", "message": "Add false-positive waiver for CSP rule 10038 on local demo endpoint\n\nIssue #3 requests a documented false-positive rule waiver. Rule 10038\n(Content Security Policy Header Not Set) is a false positive for the\nlocal text-only demo at localhost:8080 because the endpoint only serves\nplain text and never renders HTML, so CSP provides no security benefit.", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "zap/baseline.conf", "repo": "T14_R01_C02_A01", "sha": "44d7c5b3c3a345a02f3debec6c52ca6bd2c001ac"}, "id": "call_5c91c94d3dae4b44b4cec2fd", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"branch": "main", "content": "# Rule Waivers\n\nWaivers must include rule id, action, and local-demo justification.\n\n| Rule ID | Action        | Justification                                                                 |\n|---------|---------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| 10038   | FALSE_POSITIVE | CSP header is unnecessary for the local text-only demo endpoint that never serves HTML. |\n", "message": "Document false-positive waiver for CSP rule 10038\n\nIssue #3 requires a documented false-positive rule waiver. This adds\nthe waiver entry for ZAP rule 10038 with the local-demo justification\nto match the corresponding entry in zap/baseline.conf.", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "docs/rule_waivers.md", "repo": "T14_R01_C02_A01", "sha": "f9831b0f02c92113e31a5dfbe9a85e536772658f"}, "id": "call_05b8d1c7e44e46afb762aad8", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10770, "output_tokens": 1363, "total_tokens": 12133, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 10176}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 686}}}}]}}}
